{"tid":666540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三星與中興洽談芯片供應","createTime":"2018-05-16T03:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T09:19:10.000Z","uid":54870,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1f7eb844621f95b4707b71cac662939f42de8b","tid":666540,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"早前消息指中興（763）獲最重要一家供應商台灣聯發科技（MediaTek）恢復芯片供應，令中興得以「吊命」。《路透社》報道，中興再現救星，三星（SAMSUNG）的一名高層表示，公司正與中興等數家智能手機製造商洽談供應移動處理器芯片。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，正當三星尋找Exynos芯片的新客戶時，中興被美國商務部頒下七年禁運令。三星旗下邏輯芯片開發公司System LSI主管Inyup Kang表示，料明年上半年對外宣佈Exynos芯片組的新客戶。<br />\n分析員指，即使美國總統近日傳出有意放生中興的消息，但中興禁售事件顯示了其極需要多元化的供應商。三星則指尚未確定能否與中興達成協議，公司的政策對待所有供應商皆一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180516/58198249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58198249&d=duMjyfxHMcZJy4sLcEKbzMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f31ca777\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58198249&h=e84e39e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180516/58198249</a>"},{"pid":"25ea96e84eb1283ce7b46be62b4fd86025f33fd4","tid":666540,"uid":63909,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:08:12.000Z","msg":"唔會再用三星"},{"pid":"fc70169a3a915bd745c5cce5c10c6bf816ca2add","tid":666540,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"confirm 咗個deal先同我講啦!"},{"pid":"d61dde6546a4cabbfee4e4635391d0eb1bc70b69","tid":666540,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"中興點肯出二舊水既平價機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji